&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;
mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">“Managing Cognitive Biases in International Strategic
Decisions”<span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> (1995), </span>presented at the
&quot;Some New Technologies in Decision Analysis&quot; session, INFORMS
(Institute for Operations Research and the Management Sciences) International
Conference, Singapore, June.<br>
<br>
</span>“Managing Multinational Corporations in Mexico”<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">
(1994), </span>invited presentation, American Chamber of Commerce of Mexico’s
Conference on New Challenges and Opportunities under NAFTA, “Management and
Marketing” session, Monterrey, Mexico, January.<o:p>
</o:p>
<br>
<br>
“Blazing International Trails in Strategic Decision-Making Research”<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">
(1994), </span>presented at the Myers-Briggs Type Indicator and Leadership:<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>An International Conference, “International Panel” session,
University of Maryland, College Park, Maryland, January (with Rossella Pini).<o:p>
</o:p>
<br>
