Indicator and Leadership: An International Research Conference</i>, pp. 19-28.<o:p>
</o:p>
<br>
<br>
“Elea’s Vaccinations for Strategic Adaptation, Change and Renewal”<span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman">
(1993),</span><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>presented at the
“Adapting the Competence Base of Organizations” session, Thirteenth Annual
International Strategic Management Society Conference, Chicago, September (with
Rossella Pini).<o:p>
</o:p>
<br>
<br>
Session Chair/Discussant (1991) “Strategy as Perception” session, Eleventh
Annual International Strategic Management Society Conference, Toronto, October.<o:p>
</o:p>
<br>
<br>
“Cross-cultural Differences in Communication Styles”<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">
(1987), </span>presented at the Power, Negotiation &amp; Conflict Management
Interest Group, Forty-seventh Annual Meeting of the Academy of Management, New
Orleans, August.<o:p>
</o:p>
<br>
<br>
</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;
